==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Antirenter
<hw>An`ti*rent"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One opposed to
the payment of rent; esp. one of those who in 1840-47 resisted the
collection of rents claimed by the patroons from the settlers on certain
manorial lands in the State of New York.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>An`ti*rent"ism</wf> <pr>(<?/)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Antisabbatarian</ent>⟦br⟧
